===Etymology===
{{root|en|ine-pro|*weyd-}}
From {{inh|en|enm|envie}}, from {{der|en|fro|envie}}, from {{der|en|la|invidia||envy}}, from {{m|la|invidere||to look at with malice}}, from {{m|la|in-||on, upon}} + {{m|la|videre||to look, see}}.

Displaced native {{noncog|ang|æfest}}.

